FT  20 NOV 92 / Oil output rises
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
UK OIL output breached the 2m-barrel-a-day mark last month for the first
time since January. Production averaged 2.01m b/d (barrels a day), up from
1.87m b/d in September.
