Pyongyang are the carrot, Team Spirit represents the stick. Pyongyang said
at yesterday's session of the bilateral Joint Nuclear Control Commission
that it would cancel meetings with the South, including the prime ministers'
talks in December, unless Team Spirit is cancelled.
